{"title_page": "Food Wars! Shokugeki no Soma (season 5)", "text_new": "{{DISPLAYTITLE:''Food Wars! Shokugeki no Soma'' (season 5)}}\n{{Infobox television season\n |season_number= 5\n |image        = \n |caption      = \n |country      = Japan\n |num_episodes = 13\n |network      = [[Tokyo MX]], [[Nippon BS Broadcasting|BS11]], [[Animax]], [[AbemaTV]]\n |first_aired  = {{Start date|2020|4|11}}\n |last_aired   = {{End date|present}}\n |episode_list = List of Food Wars! Shokugeki no Soma episodes\n |prev_season  = [[Food Wars! Shokugeki no Soma (season 4)|Season 4]]\n}}\nThe fifth and last season of ''[[Food Wars!: Shokugeki no Soma]]'' anime television series, subtitled {{nihongo|''Food Wars! Shokugeki no Soma: The Fifth Plate''|\u98df\u621f\u306e\u30bd\u30fc\u30de \u8c6a\u30ce\u76bf|Shokugeki no S\u014dma: Go no Sara}}, was produced by [[J.C.Staff]] and directed by [[Yoshitomo Yonetani]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2020-03-22/food-wars-shokugeki-no-soma-anime-5th-season-casts-jun-fukuyama/.157797|title=Food Wars! Shokugeki no Soma Anime's 5th Season Casts Jun Fukuyama (Updated)|publisher=Anime News Network|accessdate=March 22, 2020}}</ref> The series was first broadcast in Japan on [[Tokyo MX]]. It premiered on April 11, 2020. The opening theme is \"Last Chapter\" by Nano Ripe, while the ending theme song is \"Crossing Road\" by [[Mai Fuchigami]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2020-02-09/nano.ripe-mai-fuchigami-perform-themes-for-food-wars-shokugeki-no-soma-anime-5th-season/.156244 |title=nano.RIPE, Mai Fuchigami Perform Themes for Food Wars! Shokugeki no Soma Anime's 5th Season |website=Anime News Network |date=February 9, 2020 |accessdate=February 9, 2020 }}</ref> \n\n__TOC__\n{{clear}}\n\n==Episode list==\n<onlyinclude>\n{|class=\"plainrowheaders wikitable\" style=\"width:98%; margin:auto; background:#FFF;\n|- style=\"border-bottom: 3px solid #CCF;\"\n! style=\"width:4em;\"      | {{Abbr|No.|Number}} in series\n! style=\"width:4em;\"      | {{Abbr|No.|Number}} in season\n! style=\"min-width:30em;\" | Title{{efn|English translated titles are taken from the official website.}}\n! style=\"width:12em;\"     | Original airdate\n|-\n{{Episode list/sublist\n| 1               = Food Wars! Shokugeki no Soma (season 5)\n| EpisodeNumber   = 74\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 1\n| Title           = Final Exams\n| TranslitTitle   = Gakkimatsu Shiken\n| NativeTitle     = \u5b66\u671f\u672b\u8a66\u9a13\n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|4|11}}\n| ShortSummary    = \n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist\n| 1               = Food Wars! Shokugeki no Soma (season 5)\n| EpisodeNumber   = 75\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 2\n| Title           = The BLUE Preliminaries\n| TranslitTitle   = Ao no Zensh\u014dsen\n| NativeTitle     = \u9752\u306e\u524d\u54e8\u6226\n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja\n| OriginalAirDate = {{start date|2020|4|18}}\n| ShortSummary    = \n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist\n| 1               = Food Wars! Shokugeki no Soma (season 5)\n| EpisodeNumber   = 76\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 3\n| Title           = Noir\n| TranslitTitle   = \n| NativeTitle     = \n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja\n| OriginalAirDate = {{start date|2020|5|9}}\n| ShortSummary    = \n}}<!--\n{{Episode list/sublist\n| 1               = Food Wars! Shokugeki no Soma (season 5)\n| EpisodeNumber   = 77\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 4\n| Title           = \n| TranslitTitle   = \n| NativeTitle     = \n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja\n| OriginalAirDate = \n| ShortSummary    = \n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist\n| 1               = Food Wars! Shokugeki no Soma (season 5)\n| EpisodeNumber   = 78\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 5\n| Title           = \n| TranslitTitle   = \n| NativeTitle     = \n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja\n| OriginalAirDate = \n| ShortSummary    = \n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist\n| 1               = Food Wars! Shokugeki no Soma (season 5)\n| EpisodeNumber   = 79\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 6\n| Title           = \n| TranslitTitle   = \n| NativeTitle     = 