{{cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2020-02-09/nano.ripe-mai-fuchigami-perform-themes-for-food-wars-shokugeki-no-soma-anime-5th-season/.156244 |title=nano.RIPE, Mai Fuchigami Perform Themes for Food Wars! Shokugeki no Soma Anime's 5th Season |website=Anime News Network |date=February 9, 2020 |accessdate=February 9, 2020 }}</ref> On April 17, 2020, it was announced that after the second episode, the remaining episodes of season would be delayed due to the effects of the [[2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2020-04-17/food-wars-shokugeki-no-soma-anime-delays-new-episodes-due-to-covid-19/.158711|title=Food Wars! Shokugeki no Soma Anime Delays New Episodes Due to COVID-19|publisher=Anime News Network|date=April 17, 2020|accessdate=April 18, 2020}}</ref> \n\n__TOC__\n{{clear}}\n\n==Episode list==\n<onlyinclude>\n{|class=\"plainrowheaders wikitable\" style=\"width:98%; margin:auto; background:#FFF;\n|- style=\"border-bottom: 3px solid #CCF;\"\n! style=\"width:4em;\"      | {{Abbr|No.|Number}} in series\n! style=\"width:4em;\"      | {{Abbr|No.|Number}} in season\n! style=\"min-width:30em;\" | Title{{efn|English translated titles are taken from the official website.}}\n! style=\"width:12em;\"     | Original airdate\n|-\n{{Episode list/sublist\n| 1               = Food Wars! Shokugeki no Soma (season 5)\n| EpisodeNumber   = 74\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 1\n| Title           = Final Exams\n| TranslitTitle   = Gakkimatsu Shiken\n| NativeTitle     = \u5b66\u671f\u672b\u8a66\u9a13\n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|4|11}}\n| ShortSummary    = \n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist\n| 1               = Food Wars! Shokugeki no Soma (season 5)\n| EpisodeNumber   = 75\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 2\n| Title           = The BLUE Preliminaries\n| TranslitTitle   = Ao no Zensh\u014dsen\n| NativeTitle     = \u9752\u306e\u524d\u54e8\u6226\n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja\n| OriginalAirDate = {{start date|202